                <head>No. 2<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The text of an agreement concerning United States economic and military
                    assistance to the Republic of China, effected by an exchange of notes signed at
                    Taipei on December 29, 1951 and January 2, 1952, is printed in Department of
                    State Treaties and Other International Acts Series (<gloss target="#t_TIAS1"
                        >TIAS</gloss>) 2604 or <hi rend="italic">United States Treaties and Other
                        International Agreements</hi> (<gloss target="#t_UST1">UST</gloss>), volume
                    3 (pt. 4), page 4543.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
